### **2. 30_APIRoutePulse**  
**Description:**  
Scans a list of API routes, logging uptime, latency, and status codes per route.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIRoutePulse - Endpoint Health Logger

APIRoutePulse gives quick insights into the performance of your API routes in microservices or monoliths.

## Features
- Real-time latency tracking  
- Logs status codes  
- JSON or CSV export  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_APIRoutePulse.git
cd 30_APIRoutePulse
python monitor.py
